          "audioFile": "voices/0045_ponchan.wav",
          "audioDuration": 5.013,
          "frameCount": 155
        },
        {
          "speaker": "maro",
          "text": "日本の消費量の数百年分が眠ってるのだ",
          "emotion": "normal",
          "audioFile": "voices/0046_maro.wav",
          "audioDuration": 3.413,
          "frameCount": 107
        },
        {
          "speaker": "ponchan",
          "text": "2つ目、中国は世界のレアアース供給の約70%を握ってて、輸出規制を武器にしてくるリスクがあること",
          "emotion": "serious",
          "audioFile": "voices/0047_ponchan.wav",
          "audioDuration": 7.264,
          "frameCount": 222
        },
        {
          "speaker": "maro",
          "text": "2010年の教訓を忘れちゃダメなのだ",
          "emotion": "serious",
          "audioFile": "voices/0048_maro.wav",
          "audioDuration": 2.869,
          "frameCount": 91
        },
        {
          "speaker": "ponchan",
          "text": "3つ目、中国空母のEEZ進入は資源開発への牽制であり、日本は防衛と開発の両面で対応が必要なこと",
          "emotion": "serious",
          "visual": {
            "type": "highlight",
            "text": "防衛強化×資源開発\n経済安保の両輪が不可欠"
          },
          "audioFile": "voices/0049_ponchan.wav",
          "audioDuration": 8.299,
          "frameCount": 253
        },
        {
          "speaker": "maro",
          "text": "グレーゾーン戦略に負けない体制が大事なのだ",
          "emotion": "thinking",
          "audioFile": "voices/0050_maro.wav",
          "audioDuration": 3.296,
          "frameCount": 103
        },
        {
          "speaker": "ponchan",
          "text": "そして投資家は深海採掘技術・精錬加工・レアアースユーザーの3セクターに注目してほしいの。商業化にはまだ数年かかるけど、国策テーマとして息の長い投資機会になるよ",
          "emotion": "happy",
          "visual": {
            "type": "stat",
            "value": "3セクター",
            "label": "深海採掘・精錬加工・ユーザー企業"
          },
          "audioFile": "voices/0051_ponchan.wav",
          "audioDuration": 11.733,
          "frameCount": 357
        },
        {
          "speaker": "maro",
          "text": "国策に売りなし、という格言もあるのだ",
          "emotion": "normal",
          "audioFile": "voices/0052_maro.wav",
          "audioDuration": 3.136,
          "frameCount": 99
        }
      ],
      "topic": "まとめと投資家への示唆"
    },
    {
      "type": "cta",
      "duration": 30,
      "lines": [
        {
          "speaker": "ponchan",
          "text": "次回は台湾有事シナリオと半導体サプライチェーンへの影響を深掘りするよ！",
          "emotion": "happy",
          "audioFile": "voices/0053_ponchan.wav",
          "audioDuration": 4.651,
          "frameCount": 144
        },
        {
          "speaker": "maro",
          "text": "TSMCの動きも気になるのだ",
          "emotion": "thinking",
          "audioFile": "voices/0054_maro.wav",
          "audioDuration": 2.571,
          "frameCount": 82
        },
        {
          "speaker": "ponchan",
          "text": "チャンネル登録と高評価ボタンを押してくれると嬉しいな！通知オンも忘れずにね！",
          "emotion": "happy",
          "visual": {
            "type": "keyword",
            "text": "チャンネル登録＆通知ON"
          },
          "audioFile": "voices/0055_ponchan.wav",
          "audioDuration": 4.843,
          "frameCount": 150
        },
        {
          "speaker": "maro",
          "text": "また次の動画で会おうなのだ！",
          "emotion": "happy",
          "audioFile": "voices/0056_maro.wav",
          "audioDuration": 2.048,
          "frameCount": 66
        }
      ],
      "topic": "次回予告"
    }
